Teacher Assistant

CYB1003 - Introduction to Cybersecurity

Summer 2024

I was offered the opportunity to take charge of two groups of first-year Computer Science students at the Université du Québec en Outaouais. Under the supervision of Myria Bouhaddi, Ph.D., I conducted lab sessions, where I assisted students with the following subjects:



Affine Cipher, Substitution Cipher, Polybius Square Cipher, Permutation Cipher, Vigenere Cipher, Vernam Cipher, Hill Cipher, Feistel Cipher, RSA Encryption, DES Encryption, TCP/IP Protocol, IDS/IPS, Firewall/IPtables, OCTAVE Risk Assessment, MEHARI Risk Assessment, VPN, Kali/Virtual Machines, WireShark, NMap, Metasploit.
